Then tell me.

281
00:13:30,870 --> 00:13:31,870
Tell me what to do!

282
00:13:33,670 --> 00:13:35,600
I'll do anything, anything at all,

283
00:13:35,640 --> 00:13:37,250
as long as you don't leave me!

284
00:13:50,960 --> 00:13:51,880
Really?

285
00:13:54,750 --> 00:13:55,780
Anything?

286
00:14:02,640 --> 00:14:04,410
Then carve a maple leaf here.

287
00:14:06,350 --> 00:14:07,550
Carve it with a knife.

288
00:14:11,120 --> 00:14:12,060
Can you do that?

289
00:14:14,170 --> 00:14:14,910
Yes.

290
00:15:09,790 --> 00:15:10,590
What's wrong?

291
00:15:12,360 --> 00:15:13,050
Nothing.

292
00:15:13,750 --> 00:15:15,920
I just accidentally bumped into something.

293
00:15:15,920 --> 00:15:16,520
It's fine.

294
00:15:17,910 --> 00:15:19,110
Let's eat breakfast.

295
00:15:19,200 --> 00:15:19,670
Okay.

296
00:15:35,510 --> 00:15:37,110
Let's not put up a tombstone.

297
00:15:37,870 --> 00:15:38,620
Up to you.

298
00:16:34,790 --> 00:16:35,650
Sister.

299
00:16:36,000 --> 00:16:36,390
Sister.

300
00:16:36,390 --> 00:16:37,440
I'm never coming back

301
00:16:37,440 --> 00:16:39,070
to this house again.

302
00:16:43,030 --> 00:16:43,630
Sister.

303
00:16:45,600 --> 00:16:46,360
Sister.

304
00:16:47,720 --> 00:16:48,390
Sister.

305
00:17:54,440 --> 00:17:56,040
Take it easy. We're not late.

306
00:17:56,310 --> 00:17:57,030
Take your time.

307
00:17:57,030 --> 00:17:57,440
No rush, okay?

308
00:17:57,440 --> 00:17:57,900
I'm off.

309
00:18:03,640 --> 00:18:03,920
Hello?

310
00:18:03,920 --> 00:18:05,350
Hello, is this Ms. Yan?

311
00:18:05,590 --> 00:18:07,000
Have you seen Changning?

312
00:18:07,590 --> 00:18:08,350
Nope.

313
00:18:08,920 --> 00:18:10,880
Isn't she supposed to be resting at home?

314
00:18:10,880 --> 00:18:12,110
The other day

315
00:18:12,480 --> 00:18:13,270
Changning said

316
00:18:13,270 --> 00:18:15,000
she wanted to go to grandma's
to see her little brother,

317
00:18:15,000 --> 00:18:16,510
so I let her go.

318
00:18:16,680 --> 00:18:18,640
Just now, my family called.

319
00:18:19,200 --> 00:18:20,130
Her grandma said

320
00:18:20,640 --> 00:18:21,750
she only stayed for a day

321
00:18:21,750 --> 00:18:23,150
and headed home ages ago.

322
00:18:23,400 --> 00:18:25,400
But she hasn't actually come back!

323
00:18:25,790 --> 00:18:27,270
Don't panic first.

324
00:18:28,350 --> 00:18:29,510
She took her phone

325
00:18:29,680 --> 00:18:30,980
and left with a plan.

326
00:18:31,110 --> 00:18:32,550
She must be in a clear state of mind.

327
00:18:32,550 --> 00:18:33,960
She knows exactly what she's doing.

328
00:18:33,960 --> 00:18:36,690
Let me ask some of her
other classmates too, okay?

329
00:18:36,880 --> 00:18:37,640
Okay, okay.

330
00:18:37,750 --> 00:18:38,720
Got it, Ms. Yan.

331
00:18:38,830 --> 00:18:39,830
Thank you so much!

332
00:18:40,200 --> 00:18:41,030
Hello, class.

333
00:18:41,030 --> 00:18:41,970
It's Ms. Yan.

334
00:18:42,110 --> 00:18:44,680
If anyone has any news about Li Changning,

335
00:18:45,000 --> 00:18:47,200
please let me know. Thank you!

336
00:19:14,960 --> 00:19:15,920
Why are you here?

337
00:19:17,160 --> 00:19:17,960
Where is Feng?

338
00:19:19,110 --> 00:19:20,240
-What are you doing?
-Feng!

339
00:19:20,240 --> 00:19:21,200
Get out!

340
00:19:21,200 --> 00:19:22,160
He is not here!

341
00:19:22,640 --> 00:19:23,310
-Feng!
-Stop looking!

342
00:19:23,310 --> 00:19:25,240
Don't you know he has a match today?

343
00:19:25,310 --> 00:19:26,020
Come out!

344
00:19:26,790 --> 00:19:28,270
Feng, stop hiding!

345
00:19:28,400 --> 00:19:30,000
He is not here. Stop looking.

346
00:19:30,480 --> 00:19:31,810
What are you doing here?

347
00:19:32,240 --> 00:19:34,130
Shouldn't you be back home
recovering from your illness?

348
00:19:34,130 --> 00:19:36,060
I should be the one asking you that!

349
00:19:37,400 --> 00:19:38,160
Feng said

350
00:19:38,160 --> 00:19:39,690
he can't stand your temper.

351
00:19:39,960 --> 00:19:41,400
He regrets being with you.

352
00:19:41,400 --> 00:19:42,570
He asked me to come back to be with him

353
00:19:42,570 --> 00:19:43,500
and forgive him.

354
00:19:43,640 --> 00:19:44,240
Bullshit!

355
00:19:44,910 --> 00:19:46,640
You are the one pestering Feng.

356
00:20:05,310 --> 00:20:06,330
[I really wish you were still by my side.]

357
00:20:06,350 --> 00:20:07,500
[Come back, please? Right now,
I just want to hold you tight]

358
00:20:07,520 --> 00:20:08,810
[and kiss you. Just the two of us.]

359
00:20:08,830 --> 00:20:11,270
[I find myself reliving all the beautiful
moments we shared every single second.]

360
00:20:12,590 --> 00:20:12,920
Hey!

361
00:20:39,160 --> 00:20:40,070
What is it now?

362
00:20:40,200 --> 00:20:41,460
Where is Li Changning?

363
00:20:42,590 --> 00:20:43,510
I don't know.

364
00:20:43,570 --> 00:20:44,280
Didn't she

365
00:20:44,440 --> 00:20:46,350
take a leave of absence
to recover at home?

366
00:20:46,350 --> 00:20:47,670
When was the last time

367
00:20:47,720 --> 00:20:48,640
you saw her?

368
00:20:51,320 --> 00:20:53,560
When we broke up.

369
00:20:53,590 --> 00:20:55,060
You're lying.

370
00:20:56,000 --> 00:20:56,730
Where is she?

371
00:20:59,200 --> 00:21:00,200
Suit yourself.

372
00:21:02,550 --> 00:21:03,340
Xu Feng!

373
00:21:06,600 --> 00:21:07,530
Why are you here?

374
00:21:11,220 --> 00:21:12,460
Why did you lie to me?

375
00:21:12,780 --> 00:21:14,730
Why did you go looking for
Li Changning again?

376
00:21:14,730 --> 00:21:16,020
Why?

377
00:21:16,040 --> 00:21:17,440
It was nothing but a show!

378
00:21:17,880 --> 00:21:19,130
She is crazy.

379
00:21:27,720 --> 00:21:28,250
Feng.

380
00:21:28,280 --> 00:21:29,310
Call an ambulance!

381
00:21:29,310 --> 00:21:30,390
Call an ambulance!

382
00:21:33,510 --> 00:21:34,340
Feng.

383
00:21:34,550 --> 00:21:35,420
Feng.

384
00:21:35,640 --> 00:21:37,190
I didn't mean it!

385
00:21:37,360 --> 00:21:39,140
I didn't mean it!

386
00:21:39,270 --> 00:21:40,350
It's all my fault!

387
00:21:40,400 --> 00:21:41,400
It's all my fault!

388
00:21:48,830 --> 00:21:49,750
Feng.

389
00:21:51,000 --> 00:21:51,920
Feng.

390
00:21:53,830 --> 00:21:54,750
Feng.

391
00:21:55,640 --> 00:21:56,670
Feng.

392
00:21:57,310 --> 00:21:58,400
Feng.

393
00:22:26,120 --> 00:22:27,980
Ling said she is not available today.

394
00:22:27,980 --> 00:22:28,760
I know.

395
00:22:29,030 --> 00:22:31,230
We need to verify some details with you.

396
00:22:32,280 --> 00:22:34,370
Sorry about the mess.

397
00:22:34,640 --> 00:22:35,550
Feel free to take a seat.

398
00:22:35,550 --> 00:22:36,300
Have a seat.

399
00:22:36,750 --> 00:22:37,260
You too.

400
00:22:37,480 --> 00:22:38,030
And you.

401
00:22:39,920 --> 00:22:40,940
Have some water.

402
00:22:42,070 --> 00:22:43,510
Here, drink up!

403
00:22:44,350 --> 00:22:47,350
You're pregnant. You'd better cut
down on icy drinks.

404
00:22:49,550 --> 00:22:50,950
Ling said the same thing.

405
00:22:51,560 --> 00:22:53,760
I got used to it when I was living abroad.

406
00:22:54,230 --> 00:22:55,160
I have to change.

407
00:22:55,830 --> 00:22:57,960
We have the property and partial
bank deposit documents

408
00:22:57,960 --> 00:22:59,720
under Liu Ping's name,

409
00:23:00,270 --> 00:23:01,440
plus the police inquiry records

410
00:23:01,440 --> 00:23:02,700
from your last report.

411
00:23:03,240 --> 00:23:04,640
For a better advantage

412
00:23:04,640 --> 00:23:06,400
in divorce and property division,

413
00:23:06,400 --> 00:23:07,640
we now need your

414
00:23:07,640 --> 00:23:09,880
pregnancy filing and medical records.

415
00:23:12,550 --> 00:23:15,080
Actually, I don't want
any kind of upper hand.

416
00:23:15,720 --> 00:23:18,590
I don't want to drag this out into
an ugly fight with Liu Ping,

417
00:23:18,590 --> 00:23:19,250
and I refuse

418
00:23:20,590 --> 00:23:23,320
to use our child as a bargaining
chip against him.

419
00:23:23,790 --> 00:23:24,400
So

420
00:23:25,110 --> 00:23:28,000
let's just stick to what's
written in the written pledge.

421
00:23:28,000 --> 00:23:29,240
If we go strictly by the written pledge,

422
00:23:29,240 --> 00:23:31,590
he'll basically end up
with nothing anyway.

423
00:23:31,590 --> 00:23:33,200
But we still need solid evidence

424
00:23:33,200 --> 00:23:34,930
to back up what's stated in it.

425
00:23:35,270 --> 00:23:36,550
This evidence will

426
00:23:36,590 --> 00:23:38,920
better protect your rights and interests

427
00:23:39,070 --> 00:23:41,480
So the real situation is
very important to us.

428
00:23:41,480 --> 00:23:42,270
He hit me.

429
00:23:42,270 --> 00:23:44,330
That's the absolute truth, isn't it?

430
00:23:56,210 --> 00:23:57,210
I know

431
00:23:57,640 --> 00:24:00,700
once a lawyer signs a retainer
agreement with a client,

432
00:24:01,140 --> 00:24:03,590
the lawyer is obligated to keep
everything confidential.

433
00:24:03,590 --> 00:24:06,050
Based on the principle of
zealous advocacy,

434
00:24:06,560 --> 00:24:08,310
if the client insists on sticking

435
00:24:08,310 --> 00:24:10,070
to their statement during
court cross-examination,

436
00:24:10,070 --> 00:24:11,070
the client can present

437
00:24:11,070 --> 00:24:13,640
part of the information
to the court on their own.

438
00:24:13,640 --> 00:24:14,790
The lawyer can stay out of it

439
00:24:14,790 --> 00:24:16,270
and claim no knowledge of it.

440
00:24:16,270 --> 00:24:17,000
Besides,

441
00:24:18,030 --> 00:24:19,490
isn't that why I hired you?

442
00:24:19,640 --> 00:24:20,750
I want to avoid

443
00:24:20,830 --> 00:24:22,950
going to court entirely,

444
00:24:23,070 --> 00:24:25,200
and just propose a divorce settlement

445
00:24:25,880 --> 00:24:27,480
based on his written pledge.

446
00:24:32,000 --> 00:24:33,800
Don't you agree, Attorney Zhou?

447
00:24:40,170 --> 00:24:42,430
[Emergency]

448
00:24:49,450 --> 00:24:50,150
Ms. Yan.

449
00:24:51,240 --> 00:24:52,030
Are you okay?

450
00:24:52,480 --> 00:24:53,480
I'm... I'm fine.

451
00:24:53,580 --> 00:24:54,750
How did it get this serious?

452
00:24:54,750 --> 00:24:56,150
It's all Xu Feng's blood.

453
00:24:56,310 --> 00:24:57,770
He's in surgery right now.

454
00:24:57,830 --> 00:24:58,400
Really?

455
00:24:59,200 --> 00:25:00,030
You're not hurt at all?

456
00:25:00,030 --> 00:25:00,960
Why are you here?

457
00:25:01,290 --> 00:25:03,100
Li Changning's also called me,

458
00:25:03,120 --> 00:25:04,950
so I took the earliest ride back.

459
00:25:05,680 --> 00:25:07,350
Thank you for coming all this way.

460
00:25:07,350 --> 00:25:09,680
There are still bloodstains on your neck.

461
00:25:12,580 --> 00:25:14,110
Let me wipe them off for you.

462
00:25:16,040 --> 00:25:16,560
May I?

463
00:25:18,100 --> 00:25:19,630
Okay, thanks.

464
00:25:25,480 --> 00:25:25,920
It's fine.

465
00:25:25,920 --> 00:25:27,780
I'll wash them off when I get back.

466
00:25:28,640 --> 00:25:29,970
Xu Feng's family?

467
00:25:30,110 --> 00:25:30,640
Yes, we are.

468
00:25:30,640 --> 00:25:30,920
Here.

469
00:25:30,920 --> 00:25:32,030
Xu Feng's family, right?

470
00:25:32,030 --> 00:25:32,590
Come here.

471
00:25:32,590 --> 00:25:33,200
Let me tell you,

472
00:25:33,200 --> 00:25:34,510
the surgery went smoothly.

473
00:25:34,510 --> 00:25:35,070
Fortunately,

474
00:25:35,070 --> 00:25:36,000
the stab wound was off-target

475
00:25:36,000 --> 00:25:37,510
and didn't damage any major organs.

476
00:25:37,510 --> 00:25:38,400
Still, he'll need

477
00:25:38,400 --> 00:25:39,720
quite a while to recover.

478
00:25:39,720 --> 00:25:40,160
Okay.

479
00:25:40,160 --> 00:25:41,680
Take this and go complete
the admission procedures.

480
00:25:41,680 --> 00:25:42,640
Okay, thank you.

481
00:25:44,360 --> 00:25:45,590
I've seen you both.

482
00:25:46,240 --> 00:25:48,150
You brought Xu Feng here.

483
00:25:48,440 --> 00:25:48,850
Yes.

484
00:25:48,880 --> 00:25:50,300
Thank you, thanks to you.

485
00:25:50,600 --> 00:25:52,030
For vicious assaults like this,

486
00:25:52,030 --> 00:25:53,920
that lunatic must go to jail.

487
00:25:54,040 --> 00:25:55,270
How was she even allowed on campus?

488
00:25:55,270 --> 00:25:56,680
Let's go check on our boy first.

489
00:25:56,680 --> 00:25:57,160
Okay.

490
00:25:58,680 --> 00:25:59,210
Let's go.

491
00:26:03,030 --> 00:26:05,030
It seems Xu Feng has quite a few fans.

492
00:26:11,240 --> 00:26:12,300
Is that your phone?

493
00:26:12,590 --> 00:26:13,300
Not mine.

494
00:26:18,480 --> 00:26:19,680
This is Xu Feng's bag.

495
00:26:19,880 --> 00:26:23,070
[Isolation Patient Passage]

496
00:26:23,580 --> 00:26:25,980
[Isolation Patient Passage]

497
00:26:35,080 --> 00:26:39,850
[Incoming call from Changning]

498
00:26:42,880 --> 00:26:43,550
Who is it?

499
00:26:43,790 --> 00:26:44,610
Delivery.

500
00:26:44,830 --> 00:26:45,630
Wait a minute.

501
00:26:51,550 --> 00:26:52,390
Still hiding?

502
00:26:52,610 --> 00:26:54,880
Do you have any idea how
worried sick your mom is?

503
00:26:54,880 --> 00:26:56,410
You even blocked her calls.

504
00:26:58,200 --> 00:26:59,830
Who told you this address?

505
00:27:00,070 --> 00:27:00,870
Where is Feng?

506
00:27:01,030 --> 00:27:02,460
Call your mom first,

507
00:27:02,640 --> 00:27:03,770
then we'll tell you.

508
00:27:04,340 --> 00:27:06,590
There must be something
wrong with Xu Feng.

509
00:27:06,590 --> 00:27:07,970
You think he's off too?

510
00:27:09,110 --> 00:27:10,480
Even if he's dating

511
00:27:10,480 --> 00:27:11,610
three girls at once,

512
00:27:11,960 --> 00:27:13,070
that'd only make him a lying playboy

513
00:27:13,070 --> 00:27:14,200
who gets bored easy.

514
00:27:14,720 --> 00:27:15,750
But look at these three girls,

515
00:27:15,750 --> 00:27:17,350
one's lost her mind over him,

516
00:27:17,480 --> 00:27:18,920
another might end up in jail for him,

517
00:27:18,920 --> 00:27:21,030
and the last one almost
got her face ruined.

518
00:27:21,030 --> 00:27:21,890
Is this normal?

519
00:27:23,400 --> 00:27:25,200
Even Li Changning's fallen for it too.

520
00:27:25,200 --> 00:27:26,750
I have no idea what spell she's under.

521
00:27:26,750 --> 00:27:27,880
She came back again.

522
00:27:29,750 --> 00:27:30,730
There are people

523
00:27:31,070 --> 00:27:32,680
who are experts at manipulating

524
00:27:32,680 --> 00:27:34,680
their partner's emotions
in a relationship.

525
00:27:34,680 --> 00:27:37,070
When their significant other
is obedient and loyal,

526
00:27:37,070 --> 00:27:38,880
they shower them with
praise and affection,

527
00:27:38,880 --> 00:27:40,480
making them feel utterly happy.

528
00:27:40,480 --> 00:27:41,540
If not, they punish them

529
00:27:41,540 --> 00:27:42,800
leaving them in agony.

530
00:27:43,110 --> 00:27:44,750
This repeated emotional tug-of-war

531
00:27:44,750 --> 00:27:46,680
easily makes people lose their senses.

532
00:27:46,680 --> 00:27:48,000
Gradually, they turn into

533
00:27:48,000 --> 00:27:49,930
nothing more than an obedient pet.

534
00:27:51,310 --> 00:27:53,720
But people are not pets.

535
00:27:53,960 --> 00:27:55,690
They will always try to escape.

536
00:27:56,400 --> 00:27:57,570
But what if the pain of leaving

537
00:27:57,570 --> 00:28:00,170
is so great that it makes
them lose their minds?

538
00:28:07,850 --> 00:28:09,780
Take my coat to wear on the way back.

539
00:28:09,880 --> 00:28:11,120
You're covered in blood.

540
00:28:11,120 --> 00:28:13,250
You'll scare people walking outside.

541
00:28:14,110 --> 00:28:14,790
Thank you.

542
00:28:17,510 --> 00:28:19,710
Has everything been sorted out at home?

543
00:28:20,310 --> 00:28:21,570
It's all taken care of.

544
00:28:21,680 --> 00:28:22,740
Thanks for asking.

545
00:28:23,160 --> 00:28:24,480
I've been on leave long enough.

546
00:28:24,480 --> 00:28:26,580
I still need to head back to the hospital.

547
00:28:26,580 --> 00:28:28,240
I have my car. Let me drive you.

548
00:28:28,400 --> 00:28:28,860
No need.

549
00:28:29,440 --> 00:28:31,380
You've been through a lot today
and must be exhausted.

550
00:28:31,380 --> 00:28:32,660
I'll just get a taxi.

551
00:28:33,160 --> 00:28:34,420
Besides, don't forget

552
00:28:34,510 --> 00:28:36,840
you still need to find a lawyer
for Yuan Ye.

553
00:28:40,250 --> 00:28:41,910
Alright, I'll head off first.

554
00:28:49,640 --> 00:28:50,480
Keep in touch.

555
00:28:52,030 --> 00:28:53,090
I still have so much

556
00:28:53,160 --> 00:28:54,290
to talk to you about.

557
00:28:55,550 --> 00:28:56,070
Sure.

558
00:29:09,480 --> 00:29:10,320
Yan Ling,

559
00:29:10,790 --> 00:29:12,310
we've already drafted

560
00:29:12,310 --> 00:29:13,820
Ms. Yu's divorce agreement

561
00:29:13,820 --> 00:29:15,800
and sent it to both her
and her husband today.

562
00:29:15,800 --> 00:29:17,080
If there are no issues,

563
00:29:17,270 --> 00:29:18,880
they can file for divorce

564
00:29:18,880 --> 00:29:20,940
at the Civil Affairs Bureau anytime.

565
00:29:21,110 --> 00:29:22,240
Wow, that was quick.

566
00:29:22,310 --> 00:29:23,310
Thank you so much.

567
00:29:23,620 --> 00:29:24,550
You're welcome.

568
00:29:25,590 --> 00:29:26,070
Well,

569
00:29:27,550 --> 00:29:28,570
Ms. Yu

570
00:29:28,960 --> 00:29:30,070
is actually quite capable

571
00:29:30,070 --> 00:29:31,400
of protecting herself.

572
00:29:32,680 --> 00:29:34,350
I hope she can move on soon.

573
00:29:35,240 --> 00:29:36,920
I really feel sorry for her.

574
00:29:37,330 --> 00:29:38,000
Otherwise,

575
00:29:38,270 --> 00:29:39,930
I wouldn't have bothered you.

576
00:29:41,810 --> 00:29:43,230
It's no trouble.

577
00:29:43,790 --> 00:29:44,440
Of course,

578
00:29:44,700 --> 00:29:46,790
we hope there won't
be more cases like this.

579
00:29:46,790 --> 00:29:47,400
Hey,

580
00:29:47,830 --> 00:29:49,760
I have another humble favor to ask.

581
00:29:51,440 --> 00:29:52,960
Could you refer me

582
00:29:52,960 --> 00:29:54,590
to a criminal defense lawyer?

583
00:29:54,590 --> 00:29:56,050
There's a young girl I know

584
00:29:56,200 --> 00:29:58,170
who's been detained on charges
of intentional assault.

585
00:29:58,170 --> 00:29:59,500
She's still very young,

586
00:29:59,890 --> 00:30:02,110
and I'm afraid this case
will ruin her whole life

587
00:30:02,110 --> 00:30:03,350
if it's mishandled.

588
00:30:03,940 --> 00:30:05,310
I really want to help her.

589
00:30:05,310 --> 00:30:06,200
A lawyer can only

590
00:30:06,200 --> 00:30:08,810
take the case with formal authorization
from the client or her family.

591
00:30:08,810 --> 00:30:09,920
I'll arrange a colleague to assess

592
00:30:09,920 --> 00:30:11,240
the situation tomorrow.

593
00:30:11,240 --> 00:30:11,770
Alright,

594
00:30:12,270 --> 00:30:13,150
thank you.

595
00:30:13,750 --> 00:30:14,780
Goodbye.

596
00:30:19,160 --> 00:30:19,960
What's wrong?

597
00:30:20,160 --> 00:30:20,830
What kind of people

598
00:30:20,830 --> 00:30:23,550
does Yan Ling hang around with all day?

599
00:30:24,480 --> 00:30:26,070
All those girls around her

600
00:30:26,070 --> 00:30:26,970
are so

601
00:30:27,350 --> 00:30:28,880
secretive and odd.

602
00:30:29,490 --> 00:30:30,240
I have no idea.

603
00:30:30,240 --> 00:30:31,240
It's hard to tell.

604
00:30:32,590 --> 00:30:34,450
She's just likes helping people.

605
00:30:35,060 --> 00:30:36,180
Isn't she just like you in that regard?

606
00:30:36,180 --> 00:30:37,510
Don't compare me to her.

607
00:30:38,710 --> 00:30:42,140
[Marriage Registration Office
of Civil Affairs Bureau]

608
00:30:41,270 --> 00:30:42,750
I'll take care of

609
00:30:42,770 --> 00:30:44,570
any follow-up paperwork later.

610
00:30:44,820 --> 00:30:46,680
Just call me if anything comes up.

611
00:30:47,350 --> 00:30:56,350
[Marriage Registration Office
of Civil Affairs Bureau]

612
00:30:47,400 --> 00:30:49,110
We've settled this peacefully.

613
00:30:49,110 --> 00:30:50,110
I hope you can move on

614
00:30:50,110 --> 00:30:51,240
and live a good life.

615
00:31:02,680 --> 00:31:04,210
Find someone nice someday,

616
00:31:04,440 --> 00:31:05,500
and treat her well.

617
00:31:05,730 --> 00:31:06,860
Stop drinking, too.

618
00:31:11,890 --> 00:31:14,420
I'll bring the baby to see you
after it's born,

619
00:31:14,620 --> 00:31:15,850
if you'd like.

620
00:31:17,620 --> 00:31:18,380
Xinxin.

621
00:31:20,160 --> 00:31:22,120
[Marriage Registration Office
of Civil Affairs Bureau]

622
00:31:22,360 --> 00:31:23,080
Take care.

623
00:31:28,570 --> 00:31:30,350
[Marriage Registration Office
of Civil Affairs Bureau]

624
00:31:32,000 --> 00:31:33,600
Thank you and Attorney Zhou.

625
00:31:33,800 --> 00:31:35,880
We've really put you through
a lot of trouble.

626
00:31:35,880 --> 00:31:36,750
You're welcome.

627
00:31:36,750 --> 00:31:37,680
Thank you again.

628
00:31:50,580 --> 00:31:53,330
[Marriage Registration Office
of Civil Affairs Bureau]

629
00:31:53,430 --> 00:31:56,940
[International Departure]

630
00:32:11,880 --> 00:32:14,140
Your mom will be so happy
to have you back.

631
00:32:14,640 --> 00:32:15,750
Take good care of yourself,

632
00:32:15,750 --> 00:32:17,150
and focus on recovering.

633
00:32:18,800 --> 00:32:20,400
She'll definitely blame me.

634
00:32:21,350 --> 00:32:25,010
I didn't listen to her, and now
I've learned my lesson the hard way.

635
00:32:26,470 --> 00:32:27,620
All moms say things like that.

636
00:32:27,620 --> 00:32:29,050
They're just worried.

637
00:32:29,790 --> 00:32:30,800
Deep down,

638
00:32:30,880 --> 00:32:32,480
they always love their kids,

639
00:32:33,340 --> 00:32:36,540
especially now that she's going
to be a grandmother soon.

640
00:32:42,030 --> 00:32:42,680
Thank you.

641
00:32:44,240 --> 00:32:45,900
I wish you were my real sister.

642
00:32:46,590 --> 00:32:48,720
Send me photos once the baby's born.

643
00:32:53,070 --> 00:32:54,030
I'm leaving now.

644
00:32:54,640 --> 00:32:55,440
Safe travels.

645
00:33:08,730 --> 00:33:14,340
[Reception]

646
00:33:14,860 --> 00:33:15,690
[Reception]

647
00:33:25,590 --> 00:33:26,110
Here.

648
00:33:33,110 --> 00:33:33,910
What's wrong?

649
00:33:34,240 --> 00:33:35,240
You don't want it?

650
00:33:36,350 --> 00:33:37,930
Does your wound hurt?

651
00:33:37,980 --> 00:33:39,240
Should I go get the doctor?

652
00:33:39,240 --> 00:33:39,830
No need.

653
00:33:40,480 --> 00:33:41,680
Take a look yourself.

654
00:33:42,480 --> 00:33:44,280
Is this soup or just a bowl of oil?

655
00:33:44,790 --> 00:33:47,220
I'll go home and make it again.

656
00:33:47,720 --> 00:33:49,750
Or how about I make you
some pork ribs soup?

657
00:33:49,750 --> 00:33:51,160
I don't eat pork.

658
00:33:51,550 --> 00:33:52,950
Can't you ever remember?

659
00:33:53,880 --> 00:33:54,310
You...

660
00:33:55,720 --> 00:33:57,120
Did you ever tell me that?

661
00:33:57,270 --> 00:33:58,510
Can't I say it now?

662
00:34:00,400 --> 00:34:01,660
Alright, just go home.

663
00:34:02,440 --> 00:34:03,770
I want to sleep for a bit.

664
00:34:11,800 --> 00:34:12,400
It's fine.

665
00:34:13,320 --> 00:34:14,110
I was just nearby,

666
00:34:14,110 --> 00:34:15,440
so I came to check on you.

667
00:34:15,440 --> 00:34:16,170
Don't worry.

668
00:34:16,360 --> 00:34:18,159
I won't tell anyone you're here.

669
00:34:21,670 --> 00:34:23,590
You could just get a straw for hot drinks

670
00:34:23,590 --> 00:34:24,449
and stick it in.

671
00:34:24,880 --> 00:34:26,880
That way you won't end up
drinking all the oil.

672
00:34:26,880 --> 00:34:27,810
I'll go find one.

673
00:34:55,920 --> 00:34:56,590
It's nice.

674
00:35:00,110 --> 00:35:00,800
Jealous?

675
00:35:02,030 --> 00:35:03,320
I'm just good at being born lucky,

676
00:35:03,320 --> 00:35:05,120
that's why I get a room like this.

677
00:35:05,190 --> 00:35:06,960
I'm talking about your perks.

678
00:35:08,030 --> 00:35:10,230
Good looks plus a privileged background.

679
00:35:10,230 --> 00:35:11,670
Total charm magnet.

680
00:35:12,920 --> 00:35:14,050
In just a few months,

681
00:35:14,320 --> 00:35:15,550
you've got those girls

682
00:35:15,550 --> 00:35:16,880
head over heels for you.

683
00:35:17,510 --> 00:35:18,640
You're good at this.

684
00:35:19,280 --> 00:35:20,280
Loving this, huh?

685
00:35:22,190 --> 00:35:22,990
Can't help it.

686
00:35:24,150 --> 00:35:25,810
I'm just naturally likeable.

687
00:35:26,070 --> 00:35:27,470
You don't actually think

688
00:35:28,150 --> 00:35:30,880
you're some smooth player who's
got it all figured out, do you?

689
00:35:30,880 --> 00:35:31,590
Happy now?

690
00:35:36,230 --> 00:35:37,560
What are you getting at?

691
00:35:40,320 --> 00:35:41,860
All the girls you go after

692
00:35:42,000 --> 00:35:43,330
are just barely adults,

693
00:35:44,360 --> 00:35:45,560
naive,

694
00:35:46,190 --> 00:35:47,520
from regular families.

695
00:35:48,110 --> 00:35:50,360
They lack both material comfort
and real affection.

696
00:35:50,360 --> 00:35:52,610
Give them a little warmth,

697
00:35:53,320 --> 00:35:55,120
and they fall for you right away.

698
00:35:55,950 --> 00:35:56,970
If I were you,

699
00:35:58,000 --> 00:35:59,450
preying on girls like this

700
00:35:59,450 --> 00:36:01,920
and almost getting myself
killed in the process?

701
00:36:01,920 --> 00:36:02,960
I'd be

702
00:36:03,630 --> 00:36:04,510
embarrassed.

703
00:36:10,670 --> 00:36:11,360
Found it.

704
00:36:12,590 --> 00:36:13,390
That's right.

705
00:36:13,630 --> 00:36:14,440
Use the right method,

706
00:36:14,440 --> 00:36:16,970
then you won't burn your mouth
drinking soup.

707
00:36:17,800 --> 00:36:18,460
Changning,

708
00:36:19,670 --> 00:36:20,710
think carefully

709
00:36:20,710 --> 00:36:21,970
what I told you before.

710
00:36:23,000 --> 00:36:23,800
Get well soon.

711
00:36:30,670 --> 00:36:31,800
What did he tell you?

712
00:36:35,290 --> 00:36:35,980
Speak.

713
00:36:38,150 --> 00:36:38,880
Are you mute?

714
00:36:44,000 --> 00:36:45,480
He said you don't love me.

715
00:36:53,630 --> 00:36:54,760
Do you believe him?

716
00:36:58,480 --> 00:36:58,840
I...

717
00:37:02,840 --> 00:37:03,570
have no idea.

718
00:37:04,760 --> 00:37:06,090
No idea, huh?

719
00:37:06,880 --> 00:37:08,820
Yes, he's right.

720
00:37:09,280 --> 00:37:10,320
I don't love you.

721
00:37:10,880 --> 00:37:12,400
Why aren't you leaving, then?

722
00:37:12,400 --> 00:37:14,130
Stop putting on an act here!

723
00:37:14,240 --> 00:37:14,880
I'm sorry.

724
00:37:14,920 --> 00:37:15,840
I'm sorry, Feng.

725
00:37:15,840 --> 00:37:17,260
I know you love me.

726
00:37:17,400 --> 00:37:18,800
Those messages you sent me,

727
00:37:18,800 --> 00:37:19,590
the photos,

728
00:37:19,590 --> 00:37:20,190
and the songs,

729
00:37:20,190 --> 00:37:21,360
I've seen and heard them all.

730
00:37:21,360 --> 00:37:23,590
I was just... I was just afraid
you'd leave me.

731
00:37:23,590 --> 00:37:24,280
Shut up.

732
00:37:25,360 --> 00:37:27,710
You are really annoying.

733
00:37:32,240 --> 00:37:33,840
I got stabbed just to be with you.

734
00:37:33,840 --> 00:37:34,710
And you still have the nerve to cry?

735
00:37:34,710 --> 00:37:35,630
I'm sorry.

736
00:37:38,150 --> 00:37:39,110
I'm sorry, Feng.

737
00:37:39,110 --> 00:37:39,840
I'm sorry.

738
00:37:40,070 --> 00:37:40,930
Get out.

739
00:37:41,480 --> 00:37:43,840
I'm sorry. I'll come
see you again tomorrow.

740
00:37:43,840 --> 00:37:45,240
Get some good rest first.

741
00:37:52,400 --> 00:37:54,970
[Luo Liang, Lihai Renxin Hospital]

742
00:38:00,110 --> 00:38:01,310
[Doctor Profile: Luo Liang, Male,
Associate Chief Physician]

743
00:38:01,340 --> 00:38:02,460
[Deputy Director of Outpatient
Department, Doctor of Psychiatry]

744
00:38:02,480 --> 00:38:03,050
[Master's Supervisor in Psychology]

745
00:38:03,080 --> 00:38:03,810
[National Certified Level 2
Psychological Counselor]

746
00:38:05,480 --> 00:38:06,350
Luo Liang.

747
00:38:11,390 --> 00:38:15,050
[Dongchuan Provincial Detention Center]

748
00:38:22,050 --> 00:38:22,740
Quiet.

749
00:38:35,810 --> 00:38:38,170
Regarding why Yuan Ye hurt Xu Feng,

750
00:38:38,210 --> 00:38:40,100
this is all we know so far.

751
00:38:40,440 --> 00:38:42,390
Everything points against
Yuan Ye right now.

752
00:38:40,640 --> 00:38:44,220
[Xinsheng International Law Firm]

753
00:38:44,760 --> 00:38:47,020
Is Yuan Ye still holding up emotionally?

754
00:38:47,030 --> 00:38:48,960
She said everything was her fault.

755
00:38:49,300 --> 00:38:50,720
If I go locked up,

756
00:38:51,950 --> 00:38:54,120
will Feng forgive me?

757
00:38:56,440 --> 00:38:58,570
You need to think more about yourself.

758
00:38:58,650 --> 00:39:00,740
Your whole life's still ahead of you.

759
00:39:02,210 --> 00:39:03,840
Have you ever thought about it?

760
00:39:03,840 --> 00:39:05,420
If he doesn't make it,

761
00:39:06,360 --> 00:39:07,870
you'll be a murderer.

762
00:39:09,080 --> 00:39:10,650
If Feng dies,

763
00:39:12,980 --> 00:39:15,110
I don't have anything left to live for.

764
00:39:20,360 --> 00:39:22,210
I'm so sorry, Feng.

765
00:39:22,840 --> 00:39:23,880
Should we try shifting

766
00:39:23,880 --> 00:39:24,880
our defense

767
00:39:24,880 --> 00:39:27,190
to accidental injury?

768
00:39:28,110 --> 00:39:29,960
Putting her own statement aside,

769
00:39:29,960 --> 00:39:32,380
the simple fact that
she brought the weapon

770
00:39:32,670 --> 00:39:35,330
makes it really hard to claim it
was an accident.

771
00:39:38,550 --> 00:39:40,510
I know this sounds ridiculous,

772
00:39:41,670 --> 00:39:43,040
but listen.

773
00:39:44,220 --> 00:39:45,670
One of my female students

774
00:39:46,180 --> 00:39:48,980
has already suffered terribly
because of Xu Feng.

775
00:39:49,040 --> 00:39:50,560
I just can't stand by

776
00:39:50,630 --> 00:39:51,760
and watch Yuan Ye

777
00:39:51,760 --> 00:39:53,250
go down the same path.

778
00:39:53,670 --> 00:39:54,400
Mi,

779
00:39:54,860 --> 00:39:55,320
I know

780
00:39:55,320 --> 00:39:57,320
I've caused you a lot of trouble

781
00:39:57,540 --> 00:39:59,000
and put you in a tough spot.

782
00:39:59,400 --> 00:40:01,840
But please, can you try
to think of another way?

783
00:40:01,840 --> 00:40:02,590
Don't let her ruin

784
00:40:02,590 --> 00:40:03,320
her whole life

785
00:40:03,320 --> 00:40:05,350
at such a young age

786
00:40:05,800 --> 00:40:07,230
over a guy who never even cherished her.

787
00:40:07,230 --> 00:40:08,880
she's so young.

788
00:40:18,480 --> 00:40:20,760
We've talked about this before.

789
00:40:21,450 --> 00:40:23,180
The best approach right now

790
00:40:23,200 --> 00:40:26,540
is to get the victim's forgiveness

791
00:40:26,710 --> 00:40:29,370
and offer reasonable
financial compensation.

792
00:40:29,400 --> 00:40:31,710
That's the only thing that might help

793
00:40:31,840 --> 00:40:33,170
with the final verdict.

794
00:40:34,230 --> 00:40:36,400
But looking at Yuan Ye's family situation,

795
00:40:36,400 --> 00:40:40,060
there's no way they can come up
with that much compensation money.

796
00:40:40,110 --> 00:40:42,480
Have you had any contact
with the victim's side?

797
00:40:42,480 --> 00:40:43,800
Xu Feng's family runs

798
00:40:43,800 --> 00:40:44,760
big businesses overseas.

799
00:40:44,760 --> 00:40:46,800
Small amounts of money
won't mean anything to them.

800
00:40:46,800 --> 00:40:47,760
His father had

801
00:40:47,760 --> 00:40:49,290
huge expectations for him.

802
00:40:49,300 --> 00:40:51,900
Now his son's been stabbed
for no clear reason.

803
00:40:51,990 --> 00:40:54,390
This is going to be
an extremely tough case.

804
00:41:00,710 --> 00:41:02,760
Can I be there when you talk to Xu Feng

805
00:41:03,090 --> 00:41:04,220
about a settlement?

806
00:41:12,050 --> 00:41:16,230
[The Dark Romance]

807
00:41:32,400 --> 00:41:32,960
Miss.

808
00:41:33,240 --> 00:41:34,860
Would you like some drinks, sir?

809
00:41:34,860 --> 00:41:35,560
No.

810
00:41:36,230 --> 00:41:37,900
I'd like to ask you about someone.

811
00:41:37,900 --> 00:41:39,370
She used to work here.
